      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个项目制定一个完整的甘特图，覆盖从需求到上线的全流程。我初步想分成五个阶段：规划、开发、测试、部署和文档。每个阶段要有明确的里程碑节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Planning",
        "Development",
        "Testing",
        "Deployment",
        "Documentation",
        "milestone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。关于时间格式，您希望用YYYY-MM-DD这种标准格式吗？另外，是否需要排除周末？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "excludes weekends"
